                {
                  "type": 1,
                  "content": {
                    "json": "## {eksCve} — {eksSW}\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Overview\r\n| CVE ID | Severity | CVSS 3.0 | Fix status | Published |\r\n|---|---|---|---|---|\r\n| {eksCve} | {eksCSev} | {eksCvss} | {eksFS} | {eksPub} |\r\n\r\n**CVSS vector:** {eksVec}\r\n\r\n**Vendor:** {eksVend}\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Summary\r\n{eksCvDesc}\r\n\r\n{eksExtDesc}\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Impact\r\n{eksImpact}\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Exploitability\r\n| Exploit steps published | In exploit kit | Exploit steps verified |\r\n|---|---|---|\r\n| {eksEP} | {eksEK} | {eksEV} |\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Remediation\r\n{eksRemed}\r\n\r\n**Fix version:** {eksFixVer}\r\n\r\nIf no vendor-specific guidance is shown above, update **{eksSW}** to the latest fixed version. Review running containers and deployments for instances of the vulnerable software.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### References\r\n{eksRefs}\r\n",
                    "style": "info"
                  },
                  "conditionalVisibility": {
                    "parameterName": "eksCVSel",
                    "comparison": "isEqualTo",
                    "value": "true"
                  },
                  "name": "eks_card"
                }
              ]
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "rtcloud",
              "comparison": "isEqualTo",
              "value": "aws"
            },
